as much as I find eyeshadow palettes beautiful and satisfying to look, next year is a no buy for me concerning them...i sorted out my makeup collection, sold and gave away what I didn't use, I was RUTHLESS, in the end I only kept the modern renaissance and a melt stack and that's it ! I wear winged eyeliner way more often anyways !

2020 is the year we appreciate and use what we already have instead of always wanting & buying more 😌
